;1\/2&#8243;][vc_row_inner el_class=&#8221;gt-activities-list&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;30297&#8243; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;3\/4&#8243;][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;gt-outdoor-list&#8221;]Surfing on the Gold Coast[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=&#8221;gt-activities-list&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;29182&#8243; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;3\/4&#8243;][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;gt-outdoor-list&#8221;]Hiking in the blue mountains[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=&#8221;gt-activities-list&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;28319&#8243; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;3\/4&#8243;][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;gt-outdoor-list&#8221;]Snorkeling and diving[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_id=&#8221;home-icons-section&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Travel Tips&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; el_class=&#8221;gth_home_icon_box&#8221;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;30473&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1703793908871{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Visa Information&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:p|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gtt_home_sectionOne&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Check visa requirements before traveling, ensuring a smooth entry and compliance with destination regulations.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; el_class=&#8221;gth_home_icon_box&#8221;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;30474&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1703793925702{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Health and Safety Tips&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:p|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gtt_home_sectionOne&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Prioritize health, stay hydrated, follow safety guidelines, and maintain personal hygiene for a secure journey.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; el_class=&#8221;gth_home_icon_box&#8221;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;30475&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1703793937806{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Currency and Tipping&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:p|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gtt_home_sectionOne&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Familiarize with local currency, consider customary tipping practices for respectful and seamless travel experiences.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; el_class=&#8221;float-left cta-package&#8221; el_id=&#8221;cta_section_tour&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1683730393587{background-image: url(https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tour-package-cta-yellow-background.png?id=29418) !important;}&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/4&#8243;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Share Your Ideal Tour: Let Us Customize!&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;cta_tour_heading&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/4&#8243; el_class=&#8221;display-inline-div-layer&#8221;][vc_btn title=&#8221;Enquire Now&#8221; align=&#8221;right&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1683269208464{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}&#8221; el_class=&#8221;enqu_btnmr-10&#8243; el_id=&#8221;ctaenqury&#8221;][vc_btn title=&#8221;+91 9693339999&#8243; align=&#8221;right&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1683183917329{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}&#8221; link=&#8221;url:tel%3A%2B919693339999&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row disable_element=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"st-faq-new st-faq\">\r\n    <h4>FAQs:<\/h4>\r\n                                <div class=\"item active\">\r\n                    <div class=\"header\">\r\n                        <i class=\"input-icon field-icon fa\"><svg height=\"18px\" width=\"18px\" version=\"1.1\" id=\"Layer_1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/1999\/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\"\r\n     viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"enable-background:new 0 0 24 24;\" xml:space=\"preserve\">\r\n\r\n<g fill=\"#5E6D77\">\r\n    <path d=\"M5.25,24c-0.116,0-0.232-0.027-0.336-0.079C4.659,23.793,4.5,23.536,4.5,23.25V19.5H2.25C1.009,19.5,0,18.491,0,17.25v-15\r\n        C0,1.009,1.009,0,2.25,0h19.5C22.991,0,24,1.009,24,2.25v15c0,1.241-1.009,2.25-2.25,2.25H11.5l-5.8,4.35\r\n        C5.571,23.947,5.411,24,5.25,24z M2.25,1.5C1.836,1.5,1.5,1.836,1.5,2.25v15C1.5,17.664,1.836,18,2.25,18h3\r\n        C5.664,18,6,18.336,6,18.75v3l4.8-3.6c0.129-0.097,0.289-0.15,0.45-0.15h10.5c0.414,0,0.75-0.336,0.75-0.75v-15\r\n        c0-0.414-0.336-0.75-0.75-0.75H2.25z\"\/>\r\n    <path d=\"M12,12c-0.414,0-0.75-0.336-0.75-0.75v-0.256c-0.001-0.952,0.602-1.805,1.5-2.122c0.897-0.317,1.5-1.17,1.5-2.121\r\n        c0-0.6-0.234-1.165-0.66-1.59c-0.425-0.426-0.99-0.66-1.59-0.66c-0.601,0-1.166,0.234-1.591,0.659\r\n        C9.984,5.584,9.75,6.149,9.75,6.75C9.75,7.164,9.414,7.5,9,7.5S8.25,7.163,8.25,6.75c0-2.067,1.683-3.749,3.75-3.749\r\n        c1.002,0,1.944,0.39,2.652,1.099c0.708,0.709,1.098,1.65,1.098,2.652c0,1.586-1.005,3.006-2.5,3.535\r\n        c-0.299,0.106-0.5,0.39-0.5,0.708v0.256C12.75,11.664,12.414,12,12,12z\"\/>\r\n    <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"14.625\" r=\"1.125\"\/>\r\n<\/g>\r\n<\/svg><\/i>                        <h5>Is the Maldives ideal for a family vacation? <\/h5>\r\n                        <span class=\"arrow\">\r\n                            <i class=\"fa fa-angle-down\"><\/i>\r\n                        <\/span>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                    <div class=\"body\">\r\n                        While Maldives may have gained popularity as a romantic destination, there\u2019s no doubt that it is equally family-friendly. Plenty of resorts offer kid-friendly activities like treasure hunts, quiz nights, movie nights, etc. You can also enrol your kids in a coral adoption program to sensitise them about the country\u2019s fragile environment. However, check with the tour operator if the resort allows kids, as most water villas have age restrictions.                      <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"item \">\r\n                    <div class=\"header\">\r\n                        <i class=\"input-icon field-icon fa\"><svg height=\"18px\" width=\"18px\" version=\"1.1\" id=\"Layer_1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/1999\/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\"\r\n     viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"enable-background:new 0 0 24 24;\" xml:space=\"preserve\">\r\n\r\n<g fill=\"#5E6D77\">\r\n    <path d=\"M5.25,24c-0.116,0-0.232-0.027-0.336-0.079C4.659,23.793,4.5,23.536,4.5,23.25V19.5H2.25C1.009,19.5,0,18.491,0,17.25v-15\r\n        C0,1.009,1.009,0,2.25,0h19.5C22.991,0,24,1.009,24,2.25v15c0,1.241-1.009,2.25-2.25,2.25H11.5l-5.8,4.35\r\n        C5.571,23.947,5.411,24,5.25,24z M2.25,1.5C1.836,1.5,1.5,1.836,1.5,2.25v15C1.5,17.664,1.836,18,2.25,18h3\r\n        C5.664,18,6,18.336,6,18.75v3l4.8-3.6c0.129-0.097,0.289-0.15,0.45-0.15h10.5c0.414,0,0.75-0.336,0.75-0.75v-15\r\n        c0-0.414-0.